  </h4>
</a>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 large-image">
              <div class="article-media media d-none d-sm-flex">
  <a class="vov-4-title position-relative" href="/chuong-trinh-phat-thanh/ket-noi-54/chung-tay-cuu-giup-chau-bui-thi-bao-tram-433288.vov4">
